{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "hermes-agent", "elements": [{"type": "text", "id": "t_title", "x": 300, "y": 20, "text": "任务创建400错误修复记录", "fontSize": 28, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "任务创建400错误修复记录", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "t_sub", "x": 270, "y": 60, "text": "TaskCreateSerializer assignee字段类型不匹配 | 2026-05-19", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#757575", "originalText": "TaskCreateSerializer assignee字段类型不匹配 | 2026-05-19", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "r1", "x": 60, "y": 100, "width": 220, "height": 40, "strokeColor": "#3b82f6", "backgroundColor": "#eff6ff"}, {"type": "text", "id": "t1", "x": 70, "y": 110, "text": "一、问题现象", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "一、问题现象", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s1_1", "x": 90, "y": 155, "text": "POST /api/tasks/tasks/ 返回400", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "POST /api/tasks/tasks/ 返回400", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s1_2", "x": 90, "y": 175, "text": "编辑任务(PATCH)正常，新建(POST)失败", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "编辑任务(PATCH)正常，新建(POST)失败", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s1_3", "x": 90, "y": 195, "text": "控制台: 保存任务失败", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "控制台: 保存任务失败", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "r2", "x": 60, "y": 225, "width": 220, "height": 40, "strokeColor": "#ef4444", "backgroundColor": "#fef2f2"}, {"type": "text", "id": "t2", "x": 70, "y": 235, "text": "二、根因分析", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "二、根因分析", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_1", "x": 90, "y": 280, "text": "前端发送: assignee=\"admin\" (字符串)", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "前端发送: assignee=\"admin\" (字符串)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_2", "x": 90, "y": 300, "text": "后端期望: integer pk (PrimaryKeyRelatedField)", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "后端期望: integer pk (PrimaryKeyRelatedField)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_3", "x": 90, "y": 320, "text": "类型不匹配 → 400 Bad Request", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#dc2626", "originalText": "类型不匹配 → 400 Bad Request", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_4", "x": 90, "y": 340, "text": "TaskSerializer(PATCH)已修复，TaskCreateSerializer(POST)漏了", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#b45309", "originalText": "TaskSerializer(PATCH)已修复，TaskCreateSerializer(POST)漏了", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "r3", "x": 60, "y": 370, "width": 220, "height": 40, "strokeColor": "#22c55e", "backgroundColor": "#f0fdf4"}, {"type": "text", "id": "t3", "x": 70, "y": 380, "text": "三、修复方案", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "三、修复方案", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_1", "x": 90, "y": 425, "text": "文件: apps/tasks/views.py", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "文件: apps/tasks/views.py", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_2", "x": 90, "y": 445, "text": "PrimaryKeyRelatedField → SlugRelatedField", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#16a34a", "originalText": "PrimaryKeyRelatedField → SlugRelatedField", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_3", "x": 90, "y": 465, "text": "slug_field='username'", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "slug_field='username'", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_4", "x": 90, "y": 485, "text": "validate_assignee不够(字段级检查在它之前)", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#b45309", "originalText": "validate_assignee不够(字段级检查在它之前)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "r4", "x": 350, "y": 100, "width": 280, "height": 40, "strokeColor": "#a855f7", "backgroundColor": "#faf5ff"}, {"type": "text", "id": "t4", "x": 360, "y": 110, "text": "四、涉及服务器", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "四、涉及服务器", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_1", "x": 370, "y": 155, "text": "43 (43.156.139.37)", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#7c3aed", "originalText": "43 (43.156.139.37)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_2", "x": 370, "y": 175, "text": "路径: /root/engineering-new/", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "路径: /root/engineering-new/", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_3", "x": 370, "y": 195, "text": "修复: 直接patch + gunicorn重启", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "修复: 直接patch + gunicorn重启", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_4", "x": 370, "y": 225, "text": "124 (124.222.227.28)", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#7c3aed", "originalText": "124 (124.222.227.28)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_5", "x": 370, "y": 245, "text": "路径: /home/ubuntu/engineering-new/", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "路径: /home/ubuntu/engineering-new/", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_6", "x": 370, "y": 265, "text": "修复: Python脚本+SSH base64传输", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "修复: Python脚本+SSH base64传输", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_7", "x": 370, "y": 285, "text": "重启: kill -HUP master_pid", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "重启: kill -HUP master_pid", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_8", "x": 370, "y": 305, "text": "注意: 两台服务器git HEAD不一致", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#dc2626", "originalText": "注意: 两台服务器git HEAD不一致", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "r5", "x": 350, "y": 335, "width": 280, "height": 40, "strokeColor": "#f59e0b", "backgroundColor": "#fffbeb"}, {"type": "text", "id": "t5", "x": 360, "y": 345, "text": "五、验证方法", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "五、验证方法", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s5_1", "x": 370, "y": 390, "text": "1. Django Shell: TaskCreateSerializer.is_valid()", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "1. Django Shell: TaskCreateSerializer.is_valid()", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s5_2", "x": 370, "y": 410, "text": "2. HTTP API: curl POST /api/tasks/tasks/", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "2. HTTP API: curl POST /api/tasks/tasks/", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s5_3", "x": 370, "y": 430, "text": "3. 浏览器UI: 任务看板 → 新建 → 保存", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "3. 浏览器UI: 任务看板 → 新建 → 保存", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s5_4", "x": 370, "y": 450, "text": "关键验证点: assignee传\"admin\"不再400", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#16a34a", "originalText": "关键验证点: assignee传\"admin\"不再400", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "r6", "x": 350, "y": 470, "width": 280, "height": 40, "strokeColor": "#64748b", "backgroundColor": "#f8fafc"}, {"type": "text", "id": "t6", "x": 360, "y": 480, "text": "六、经验教训", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "originalText": "六、经验教训", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s6_1", "x": 370, "y": 525, "text": "1. 修同类问题时举一反三，避免遗漏", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "1. 修同类问题时举一反三，避免遗漏", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s6_2", "x": 370, "y": 545, "text": "2. HUP重载对代码修改不一定生效", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "2. HUP重载对代码修改不一定生效", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s6_3", "x": 370, "y": 565, "text": "3. Serializer字段默认行为要警惕", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "3. Serializer字段默认行为要警惕", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s6_4", "x": 370, "y": 585, "text": "4. 两台服务器代码应保持同步", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#374151", "originalText": "4. 两台服务器代码应保持同步", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "doc_link", "x": 60, "y": 520, "text": "详细文档: docs/TASK_CREATE_BUG_FIX_2026-05-19.md", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#6b7280", "originalText": "详细文档: docs/TASK_CREATE_BUG_FIX_2026-05-19.md", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "rect_985", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "x": 30, "y": 985, "width": 900, "height": 50, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_923", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "财务页面年份选择器 + 统计数字修复 | 2026-05-19", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 923, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1083", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "一、问题现象", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1083, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1111", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "收入/支出/报表管理页面打开后：年份选择器显示\"加载中\"，统计数字为 ¥0", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1111, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1139", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "手动刷新页面或等待数秒后数据部分恢复，但年份下拉仍异常", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1139, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1167", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1167, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1195", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "二、根因（两条独立 bug，必须同时修复）", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1195, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1223", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "根因 A — Bootstrap-select class 缺失：#filterYear 缺少 selectpicker class", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1223, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1251", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "  → loadYearOptions() 末尾条件 if (classList.contains('selectpicker')) 不满足", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1251, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1279", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "  → $(select).selectpicker() 不调用，select 外观不渲染，显示\"加载中\"", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1279, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1307", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "根因 B — 权限未分配：finance:report:read 从未分配给任何角色", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1307, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1335", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "  → /api/finance/reports/years/ 返回 403", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1335, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1363", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "  → loadYearOptions() 抛出异常 → catch 块清空已填充的 select（expense）或 stats 未更新", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1363, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1391", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1391, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1419", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "三、涉及文件（124 验证修复）", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1419, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1447", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "A1. income_list.html L142：filterYear 加 class=\"selectpicker\"", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1447, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1475", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "A2. expense_list.html L434：loadYearOptions catch 块移除 select.innerHTML 清空行", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1475, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1503", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "A3. report_dashboard.html L122：filterYear 加 selectpicker；L315：catch 后加 $(select).selectpicker('refresh')", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1503, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1531", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "B. DB core_role_permission：finance:report:read 分配给 系统管理员/部门经理/普通员工/财务", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1531, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1559", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "C. settings_pg.py：ALLOWED_HOSTS IP 修正（124 为 124.222.227.28）", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1559, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1587", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1587, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1615", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "四、同步结果", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1615, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1643", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "43 (43.156.139.37) ✅：views.py + 3个模板 + DB权限 + gunicorn重启", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1643, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1671", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "129 (129.204.250.24) ✅：views.py + 3个模板 + DB权限 + gunicorn重启", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1671, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1699", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1699, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1727", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "五、验证方法", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1727, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1755", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "curl http://目标:8001/api/core/health/ → {status:ok}", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1755, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1783", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "curl 带 cookie http://目标:8001/api/finance/reports/years/ → 200（不是403）", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1783, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1811", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "浏览器打开 /finance/incomes/ → 年份立即显示\"2026年\"，无需操作", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1811, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1839", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "浏览器打开 /finance/expenses/ → 统计 ¥500,810.55，本年117笔", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1839, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1867", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "浏览器打开 /finance/reports/ → 月度报表立即渲染，¥249,792.91 / ¥501,105.65", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1867, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1895", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1895, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1923", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "六、经验教训", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1923, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1951", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "1. 同一个表象（年份\"加载中\" + ¥0）可能有多个独立根因，必须同时修复", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1951, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_1979", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "2. Bootstrap-select 条件判断：必须有 class='selectpicker' 才调用 .selectpicker()", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 1979, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_2007", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "3. catch 块内不要清空已成功填充的 DOM，只做降级处理", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 2007, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_2035", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "4. 新增权限后必须同步分配给已有角色，不能只建权限不分配", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 2035, "angle": 0}, {"type": "text", "version": 1, "isDeleted": false, "id": "new_2063", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "text": "5. 年份/日期选择器出问题优先查 API 响应码和网络面板", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "baseline": 14, "x": 50, "y": 2063, "angle": 0}]}